Ousman Jatta married wife Beryl in Gambia 13 years ago . 
  He took her to a care home in February while he went to Africa for three weeks . 
  But when he returned he was not allowed to take her home with him by Bristol City Council . 
  Mr Jatta moved back to the UK with his wife when she became ill with dementia . 
  He has threatened to go on hunger strike unless council hand over wife . 
  He says she has pleaded to return home to him . 
 